  ('dietitian-moex-04686', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於人體腎素-血管收縮素（renin-angiotensin）系統的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["腎素（renin）作用於 alpha-腎上腺素受器（alpha-adrenergic receptor）將血管收縮素原 （angiotensinogen）水解為血管收縮素I（angiotensinI）", "血管收縮素I（angiotensinI）可透過血管收縮素轉換酶（angiotensin-convertingenzyme）形成血 管收縮素II（angiotensinII）", "血管收縮素II（angiotensinII）可透過cyclicAMP訊號傳遞路徑調節血壓", "血管收縮素II（angiotensinII）可繼續轉變成調節血壓活性更強之血管收縮素III（angiotensinIII）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a95b04b12138", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2f7c57b169bb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "101", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
